Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35\fad(200,200)}翻譯：aegis   後期：神様
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17號 6號 配置完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗體生命反應正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sacred特殊能力發動無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17號站起來 束縛解除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束縛解除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所長 准備完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就開始吧 輝島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:01:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 讓我看到你更強的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17號透明度（Clarity）數值上升2.5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6號正在那個區域內釋放能量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我失望啊 輝島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量應該不止於此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還缺少覺悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17號爆發了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等這一刻好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直在等待這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17號企圖脫離管制區域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入二級警備狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好准備 屋頂電流最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要沖進他們中間去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別離開我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 讓他們跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 反正遲早會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們各位都是可靠的贊助商
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你們的福獨眼巨人（Cyclops）的開發非常順利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個舞會算是餞別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻給讓他沉睡的力量覺醒的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 盡情使用sacred的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和同樣從石中誕生的同胞一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 好像還有不速之客呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美 你一定要由我親手...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到治療時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有研美的藥竟然就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出研究所已經一年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們至今仍被他束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來日本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是研美？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做你的保鏢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我很閑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖石檢察官（Sacred Passer）？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 來觀察我有沒有資格登上神座的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美 今天一定要把你...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家夥和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個我更在意那邊的惡石反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的石子們開始滾動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到除了我們還有幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你去殺研美了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就待在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我也可以戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥 會變成我們的敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊我們的是一個叫輝島奈特的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了抓住他 能借助你們的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了幾個麻煩的角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 為了活下去無論如何我都需要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 來了 來了鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪先生 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近了 錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝之記憶 吾心長存
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之意志 獻於汝身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是聖石解放（Sacred Liberation）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美先生 輝島進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為我特別定制的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是個麻煩的家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這點困難都克服不了怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧 輝島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓你繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 戰鬥吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此提高吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是解放者（Liberator）的力量 有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪 丹童子阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 貫通萬物的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 惡石的事件真的是你引起的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的力量不屬於任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果失去自由的翅膀也會自尋死路的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這家夥挺能幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們又穿過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很中意這只耳朵的 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中能幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成長到什麼地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信研美那家夥 和我.... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我需要你的力量 丹童子阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 大小姐失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 只能靠他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 還活在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被綁架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 琉璃被綁架了嗎鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 來吧 追著我的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丹童子阿爾瑪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝島奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你真相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽小姐沒事吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 聽到我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不制造這種情況就沒法和你好好談談了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做我的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們擁有相同的力量 沒有敵對的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做你的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我們這邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺掉研美重獲自由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我視而不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子阿爾瑪 你為什麼而戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家夥沒有自己的意志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了贏得自由而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉 你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝島 對他你是下不了手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥..哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 紅玉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懼怕sacred力量的父母把我賣給了研美的研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後 初來乍到的我就和其他能力者發生沖突
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 要洗幹淨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有不可以糟蹋糧食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長不大的哦 小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為哥哥很高大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠很快也會長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我很討厭這個油嘴滑舌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這裏的編號 是你真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特 輝島奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特嗎 是個保護別人的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來你會要保護誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比其他能力者 紅玉一直很關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當翡翠感到寂寞哭泣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉一定會給他講名叫青蛙公主的俄羅斯童話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果變成青蛙 王子就會來救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我變成青蛙 哥哥會來救我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我會變成王子去救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然平靜的日子持續了一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從那一天起風雲突變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰她 別碰翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉第一次覺醒的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被分開 開始了被強迫戰鬥的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要吃這藥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話 全部吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 別碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17號 從今天起1號和你住一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈..奈特 王子...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特 王子...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候 我和翡翠並不知道那是紅玉身為人類的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聖誕夜 劉紅玉死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天提升到什麼級別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 人格會崩壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對他也比較幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那一天發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 紅玉回來的時候已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 肉體還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然精神活動已經停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的他只是被猛獸附體的怪物罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把我們能力者稱為怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成惡石無法複原的狀態稱為怪物不正合適麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 過去被稱為紅玉的存在已經不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉 我來斬斷你的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把0號放出去真是個危險的賭注呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0號居然會認出翡翠的確是在計劃之外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣究竟能不能排除我們的嫌疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是時候了 准備打出新的王牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時靜觀其變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼 請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥不是死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠 紅玉已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.86,0:24:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能做的只有把他從研美手中解放出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.11,0:24:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思 難道要把哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 至少由我親手把他...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.71,0:24:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.10,0:24:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥只是因為研美的魔法不能變回人類
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.21,0:24:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有血清一定能變回...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.38,0:24:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 紅玉已經變不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.91,0:24:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奈特不能就哥哥的話 那我來成為王子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.11,0:24:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成王子去救哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.49,0:24:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.28,0:24:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有紅玉變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.92,0:25:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他自己的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和翡翠之所以能繼續待在研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.14,0:25:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為紅玉自己答應獻身實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.35,0:25:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...一直被他保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.79,0:25:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我連保護她都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.53,0:25:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久我也不是人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.10,0:25:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 只有我的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.04,0:25:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有琉璃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.79,0:25:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美悠士的計劃好像已經進入最終階段了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.38,0:25:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周前出現在三浦出現的2個惡石
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.86,0:25:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也是受到研美的操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.24,0:25:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒他們的丹童子阿爾瑪的力量有了大幅提升吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.61,0:26:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 這力量是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.37,0:26:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒有覺悟的家夥為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.49,0:26:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.99,0:26:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥居然有這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.30,0:26:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼 什麼改變了 丹童子阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.10,0:26:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個自以為是的家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.57,0:26:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.82,0:27:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是你還是藍羽琉璃只是被人利用而已
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.94,0:27:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被沒有力量軟弱而又卑劣的人類利用
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.79,0:27:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由吧 丹童子阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.27,0:27:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為人類賣命 得到幾句感謝 獲得狹窄的住所
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的生活有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.70,0:27:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不想得到感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.78,0:27:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很高興而已
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.43,0:27:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我只能用於破壞的力量能幫助別人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.90,0:27:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護別人 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.57,0:27:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是為此感到高興而已
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.10,0:27:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才終於能認同自己
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.22,0:27:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量也有存在的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.01,0:27:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.96,0:27:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特 不和我們一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.98,0:27:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有著相同的力量 那麼你也成為同伴...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.56,0:27:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要殺了研美
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.39,0:28:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界沒你想象的那麼單純
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.89,0:28:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁有相同的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.84,0:28:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺在我和你眼前的路卻是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.32,0:28:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有想要守護的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.25,0:28:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的力量有其存在的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.08,0:28:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護別人而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.85,0:28:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護別人這種事根本做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.84,0:28:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.70,0:28:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要保護她 但是做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.27,0:28:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經回不了頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.61,0:28:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真心想要保護嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.97,0:28:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.31,0:28:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你是真心的就一定能保護好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.10,0:28:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得好像什麼都知道一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.74,0:28:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.55,0:28:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會懂 你怎麼可能明白我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.30,0:29:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我們一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.52,0:29:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能像這樣 將對手打碎殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.41,0:29:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.09,0:29:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我 要守護
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.62,0:29:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.71,0:29:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.29,0:29:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.75,0:29:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 阿爾瑪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.76,0:29:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.66,0:30:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠缺的或許正是覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.14,0:30:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我所能做的 就是為了讓翡翠的得到自由
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.02,0:30:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使同歸於盡也要把研美殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.92,0:30:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.37,0:30:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 之前的調查有結果了 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.46,0:30:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 對各部門放出嫌疑情報
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.62,0:30:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓藍羽家無法在社會上立足
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.03,0:30:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是想利用這陣騷動抓住能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.36,0:30:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.40,0:30:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都如他的預料
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.74,0:30:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是時候了 准備打出新的王牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.13,0:30:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的挺能幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.57,0:30:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼艱難的時候還打算一個人承擔一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.83,0:31:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大聲說話
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.54,0:31:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是研美的部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.45,0:31:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.39,0:31:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等待時機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.32,0:31:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 已經醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.34,0:31:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.63,0:31:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.50,0:31:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標兩名已經捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.73,0:31:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女高中生什麼的最討厭了鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.55,0:31:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.72,0:31:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.20,0:31:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是最後一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.00,0:31:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍放下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.65,0:31:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搶我的風頭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.88,0:31:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.41,0:31:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦的哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.08,0:31:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開警察的耳目把這些搬到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.15,0:31:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女僕隊 集合完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.08,0:32:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約裝甲的准備也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.77,0:32:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該已經被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.36,0:32:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經和藍羽沒關系了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.97,0:32:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 所以這是我們憑自己的意志要這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.78,0:32:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經不是藍羽家的人了 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.62,0:32:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不會聽鏡先生的指示哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.21,0:32:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也想救出大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.91,0:32:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 請讓我們陪你到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.66,0:32:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們是這麼說的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.50,0:32:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群傻瓜...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.59,0:32:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.28,0:32:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 帶我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.89,0:32:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中南美建立起巨大帝國的阿茲泰克人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.68,0:33:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重複的戰爭中 挖走了數萬俘虜的心臓
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.12,0:33:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.86,0:33:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 阿爾瑪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.11,0:33:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美所長
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.79,0:33:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然開始了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.56,0:33:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准備獨眼巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.22,0:33:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.02,0:33:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特入侵進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.58,0:33:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方有疑似運輸卡車的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.65,0:33:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是完全照劇本發展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.27,0:33:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.54,0:33:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保鏢遊戲就到這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.76,0:34:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.84,0:34:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.14,0:34:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.37,0:34:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還愣著幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.17,0:34:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少礙事 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.14,0:34:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉 現在就讓你解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.77,0:35:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.75,0:35:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.19,0:35:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.57,0:35:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 他已經不能變回人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.52,0:35:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是在被研美利用之前讓他解脫比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.45,0:35:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把血清帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.90,0:35:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個讓哥哥... 拜托了 奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.01,0:35:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.09,0:35:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.39,0:35:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好像防禦本能無法停止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.17,0:35:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 琉璃就變不回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.99,0:35:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快回來 藍羽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.08,0:36:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 讓我的聲音...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.26,0:36:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意志 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.30,0:36:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達到吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.91,0:36:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.77,0:36:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 紅玉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.80,0:36:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.86,0:37:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好像蘊藏著超出我預期的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.40,0:37:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.76,0:37:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.35,0:37:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你們提升至今的能量就由我...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.60,0:37:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.11,0:37:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰她 別碰她 別碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.84,0:37:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠 奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.51,0:37:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.90,0:38:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 紅玉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.09,0:38:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 雜碎們
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.28,0:38:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥給我留下了很棒的東西哦 歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.39,0:38:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.72,0:38:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就能與神對等了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.25,0:38:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.66,0:38:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.17,0:38:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全身的每一塊肌肉都在興奮的顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.36,0:39:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無敵了 這就是無敵的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.03,0:39:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sacred的力量實在太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.97,0:39:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉這種雜碎就有這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.77,0:39:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主菜就讓我吃了你吧 丹童子阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.83,0:39:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再把琉璃當甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.43,0:39:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時我就會登上神之座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.70,0:39:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神之座與你無緣 我來送你下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.48,0:39:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 我也會吃了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.76,0:39:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個雜碎一起
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.67,0:39:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.26,0:40:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.77,0:40:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝島
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.03,0:40:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許東張西望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.02,0:40:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的動作... 是在誘導我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.03,0:40:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.81,0:40:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜碎也能派上用場真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.46,0:40:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 怎麼不反擊 你這窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.97,0:40:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強吧 高純度的sacred的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.98,0:40:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的力量 是你從紅玉身上奪走的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.34,0:40:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了紅玉也要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.91,0:41:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝島 你這種空虛的人得到sacred的力量也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.75,0:41:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強大的力量對只有像我這種有理念的人才有用
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.54,0:41:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說笑了 你不過是在利用別人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.00,0:41:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也只是想對我進行個人的複仇麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.85,0:41:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.80,0:41:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.05,0:41:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說這是變廢為寶
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.80,0:41:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特 別管我 殺了研美
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.39,0:41:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 接下來只能肉搏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.87,0:41:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的目的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.51,0:41:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你挺能幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.93,0:41:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.03,0:41:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡先生 我們找到琉璃大小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.90,0:42:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有5人正在保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.91,0:42:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 你們就這樣和大小姐一起撤出研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.90,0:42:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.21,0:42:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.67,0:42:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的就只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.64,0:42:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好保護睡美人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.89,0:42:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不是要殺了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.20,0:42:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的覺悟也只有這種程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.63,0:42:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 奈特是因為我...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.87,0:42:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有我在.... 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.16,0:42:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我.... 太沒用了 只會礙事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.04,0:43:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美 殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.09,0:43:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣奈特就能自由戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.99,0:43:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來雜碎還更明白事理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.44,0:43:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我來實現你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.74,0:43:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.72,0:43:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.95,0:43:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.06,0:43:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.10,0:43:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能見到哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.54,0:43:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.91,0:43:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.12,0:43:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.82,0:44:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.70,0:44:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.77,0:44:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.34,0:44:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是sacred seven的究極力量
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.91,0:44:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.83,0:44:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.95,0:45:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.86,0:45:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論研美 還是我 全部消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.38,0:45:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量 好想要 好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.54,0:45:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 消失吧 消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.05,0:46:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.54,0:46:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.54,0:46:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你不用戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.37,0:46:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 不能變身
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.33,0:46:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.56,0:46:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠 不能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.51,0:46:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.81,0:46:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最棒的塗裝到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.06,0:46:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想殺了研美反而幫了他
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.92,0:46:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不覺得會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.03,0:47:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太蠢了 我還是消失不見的好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.42,0:47:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.01,0:47:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄掙紮 老老實實讓我吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.13,0:47:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上我就要得到究極的sacred seven了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.88,0:47:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄掙紮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.68,0:47:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論多堅硬都能破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.34,0:48:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中一點 極限的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.41,0:48:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.51,0:48:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.43,0:48:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事可不在計劃之內
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.54,0:48:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一切都盡在掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.43,0:48:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.09,0:48:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 沒錯吧 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.26,0:48:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我完了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.47,0:48:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把紅玉和我的惡意都給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.41,0:49:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現你的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.33,0:49:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.61,0:49:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.22,0:49:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.98,0:49:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.19,0:49:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠 用你的惡意將世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.22,0:50:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.50,0:50:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.58,0:50:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要 因為我 哥哥才變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.92,0:50:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特也... 大家都受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.76,0:50:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能存在於世 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.53,0:50:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這種時候我什麼都做不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.20,0:50:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.56,0:50:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.51,0:50:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救救她吧 和阿爾瑪一起
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.67,0:50:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪先生明白翡翠的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.02,0:50:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有他是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.22,0:51:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直和她在一起的你也是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.02,0:51:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.08,0:51:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.35,0:51:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.17,0:51:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝之記憶 吾心永存
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.37,0:51:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之意志 獻於汝身
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.33,0:51:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把惡意之核從她體內取出來
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.14,0:51:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.25,0:51:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.90,0:51:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.56,0:51:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.68,0:51:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能到翡翠身邊...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.08,0:51:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.72,0:51:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.58,0:51:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.21,0:51:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.99,0:52:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 我還是不在的好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.36,0:52:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.16,0:52:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一心想著保護你 卻一直沒有正視你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.24,0:52:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你一直處於不安之中
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.06,0:52:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我會認真的面對你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.45,0:52:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.33,0:52:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說想消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.23,0:52:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.17,0:53:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅玉 你自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.70,0:53:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.31,0:53:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.63,0:53:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠了你不小的人情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.14,0:53:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.64,0:53:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會還你的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.66,0:53:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事沒關系的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.61,0:53:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今後想怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.13,0:53:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會去尋找屬於我們的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.97,0:53:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也回到你的歸宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.75,0:58:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜 你失去資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.69,0:58:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.23,0:58:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是拉克尼 日本的調查結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.42,0:58:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 接下來我就回神之座了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.42,0:58:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.08,0:59:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠他們不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.56,0:59:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 他們一定會找到自己的歸宿的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.56,0:59:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.09,0:59:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是啊 阿爾瑪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.03,0:59:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 一定沒問題的
